docs.lead_paragraph: HAMBURG, Dec. 26 (Associated Press)--Germany's foreign trade relations, which in 1919 gave some promise of gradual and substantial improvement, suffered disastrously during 1920, the Hamburg Chamber of Commerce says in the annual report which is to be published tomorrow.

docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Dec. 28.-- Secretary Colby and his party arrived at Montevideo this afternoon at 4 o'clock. The Florida anchored ten miles out. The American Minister, the Foreign Minister and the Admiral of the Uruguayan fleet and his staff came out on a gunboat to meet the Florida, accompanied by airplanes.
